OL,3,CUnder fire South East Water boss
OL,4,Cresigns in wake of major outage
OL,6,FThe under fire boss of South East
OL,7,FWater has resigned following a series
OL,8,Fof outages which left thousands of
OL,9,Fpeople with no supply.
OL,11,FDavid Hinton had come under increasing
OL,12,Fpressure to step down following the
OL,13,Fcrisis which began in the lead up to
OL,14,FChristmas.
OL,16,FOn Friday South East Water confirmed
OL,17,FMr Hinton's resignation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
