PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778256667
OL,3,CUnder fire South East Water boss
OL,4,Cresigns in wake of major outage
OL,6,FIn a statement a spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"He will remain in post to allow an
OL,8,Forderly transition over the summer
OL,9,Fperiod and continued momentum of the
OL,10,Ftransformation plan while the Board
OL,11,Fundertakes the process of finding a
OL,12,Freplacement.
OL,14,F"Further details will be announced in
OL,15,Fdue course.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
