OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778256667
OL,3,CUnder fire South East Water boss
OL,4,Cresigns in wake of major outage
OL,6,F"Mr Hinton has decided to step down as
OL,7,Fhe feels his position has become an
OL,8,Fincreasing distraction from South East
OL,9,FWater's most important priority, which
OL,10,Fis to deliver a resilient water supply
OL,11,Ffor its customers.
OL,13,F"The Board remains focused on
OL,14,Faccelerating targeted engineering
OL,15,Fworks and making operational changes
OL,16,Fto improve the resilience of the
OL,17,Fsupply network, increase water
OL,18,Fcapacity and quality in high priority
OL,19,Fareas as part of a comprehensive,
OL,20,FCompany-wide transformation plan."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
