OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778256667
OL,3,CUnder fire South East Water boss
OL,4,Cresigns in wake of major outage
OL,6,FLisa Clement, Interim Independent Non-
OL,7,FExecutive Chair, said: "The Board
OL,8,Facknowledges and thanks Dave for his
OL,9,Fmany years of loyal dedication and
OL,10,Fservice to South East Water."
OL,12,FMore follows.
